   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "### 3a. Feature creation\n",
    "\n",
    "The inputs are mostly anonymised PCA components, so feature *creation* is limited - but we can build two\n",
    "interpretable features and, crucially, **measure** whether they help: `Hour` (from `Time`) and `log_Amount`\n",
    "(a log transform to tame Amount's heavy right tail). We add them to XGBoost and compare PR-AUC."
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 22,
   "metadata": {},
