   "source": [
    "### Experiment 1 - The accuracy illusion\n",
    "\n",
    "Accuracy on a 0.17%-fraud problem is dominated by the legitimate class. We compare every model's accuracy to a\n",
    "model that simply **never predicts fraud**, and then show that accuracy cannot tell the models apart while\n",
    "PR-AUC can. We also trace how the best model's **precision depends on the base rate** it is deployed at."
   ]
  },
